{{en-noun|helm|helms}}

#(''Nautical'') The [[steering gear]] of a [[ship]], especially the [[tiller]] or [[wheel]].
#(''Yachting'') The member of the [[crew]] in charge of [[steer]]ing the [[boat]].
#(''Metaphorical'') A [[position]] of [[leadership]] or [[control]].

